Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:06.13,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gundam久违19年的 完全新作电影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让世界融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多必须要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们面前到底有多少 必须要跨越的试炼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:17.87,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}未知之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你们有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能让你们从这过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙曼大尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一个被确认的变革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是想知道 变革者的实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.10,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}新人类（变革者）的觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯·阿尔马克！为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:39.63,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}伊奥利亚计划 最终阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「即将到来的对话」…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 这是天人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我们剩下的最后任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「即将到来的对话」开始 那将是人类的觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了终结战争的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是刹那渴求的Gundam 00 QAN[T]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感受他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的思念 将人们维系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底为了什么来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让刹那死在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 开拓未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上人类的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终决战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧场版机动战士Gundam 00
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离人类灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有7日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们 什么时候才能互相理解
